Understanding the B2B Growth Stack
The B2B Growth Stack refers to the integration of three core components working in harmony: Account-Based Marketing (ABM), Demand Generation (DemandGen), and Generative AI (GenAI). Rather than operating in silos, these three elements create a unified system where each component strengthens the others.

Think of it this way: demand generation identifies and attracts your ideal customers, ABM personalizes the engagement for high-value accounts, and GenAI optimizes every step by analyzing data, predicting outcomes, and automating repetitive tasks. When orchestrated properly, this stack transforms how B2B organizations approach revenue generation.

