What is Account-Based Marketing (ABM)?
Account-Based Marketing is a strategic approach where sales and marketing teams align to target specific, high-value accounts with personalized campaigns. Instead of treating all prospects equally, ABM identifies accounts that fit your ideal customer profile and tailors every interaction to their unique needs, challenges, and buying stage.

