How ABM Works
The ABM process typically follows this sequence:

Identify: Define your ideal customer profile (ICP) and select target accounts based on firmographic data, technographic signals, and buying intent indicators.

Engage: Develop personalized content, messaging, and experiences designed specifically for each target account and their key stakeholders.

Convert: Execute coordinated sales and marketing efforts to move accounts through the sales cycle and close deals faster.

Expand: Once a customer is signed, continue account-based strategies to identify upsell and cross-sell opportunities.

